        <h2>Terms and Policies</h2>
        <p>
            - Year quantity for a timeshare is 10 years by default.
        </p>
        <p>- Reservation fee is 500.000VND. This fee must be paid before the property is officially offered for sale; else, your reservation will be instantly canceled.</p>
