        <p> - Reservation fee for all properties are 500,000 VND each.</p>
        <p>
            - Deposit fee is 10% of total fee.
        <p>
            - Our total fee will be divided into 3 terms:
        </p>
        <p>
            + First term: you must pay within 7 days from the day you pay the deposit fee
        </p>
        <p>
            + Second term: you must pay within 1 year from the day you pay the deposit fee
        </p>
        <p>
            + Third term: you must pay within 2 year from the day you pay the deposit fee
        </p>
        </p>
